    "en": {
      "title": "is secure; It is also scary",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A phone call to the public number of the Presidential Secretariat said that he had the Buddha statue and books stolen from President Ranil Wickremesinghe's residence.",
        "The caller said that he is afraid to keep the stolen Buddha statue and books and should return them to the owner.",
        "The person on the phone who said the Buddha statue and books were safe said he wanted to speak to the president's secretary.",
        "After receiving the information through a call from the President's Secretariat, the officer reported the matter to the President's Secretary, and the Secretary handed over further investigations to the Criminal Investigation Department."
      ],
